    "Designers will then be able to add further details to these samples to produce a richly textured digital garment.",
    "Such a system could greatly improve the working efficiency of designers, and could enable users to create personalized products based on their preferences.",
    "Depending on the type of input, fashion design can be divided into single-modal and multi-modal processes.",
    "The aim of single-modal fashion design is to transfer visual elements (such as colors, textures, etc.)",
